Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.63,0:01:10.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.63,0:01:10.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.92,0:01:12.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先生对不起  我们关
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:12.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sir, we're closed
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.59,0:01:13.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.59,0:01:13.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy, there, Krusty Krab--
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.97,0:01:14.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要什么服务
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.97,0:01:14.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How can I help you?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.55,0:01:16.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,匹萨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:16.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pizza?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.84,0:01:18.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然有匹萨了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:18.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course we have pizza
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.39,0:01:19.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.39,0:01:19.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.26,0:01:21.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的章鱼外卖员马上给您送到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:21.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our delivery squid will bring it right over
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.31,0:01:24.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我们不卖匹萨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:24.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krab, we don't serve pizza
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.15,0:01:29.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(481.557,798)}匹萨
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.02,0:01:30.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们不外卖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.02,0:01:30.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We don't deliver
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.61,0:01:32.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是不外卖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:32.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We don't deliver
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.15,0:01:33.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但外卖的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:33.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you do
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.11,0:01:37.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就不能让海绵宝宝去送外卖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:37.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't you just get SpongeBob to do it?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.57,0:01:38.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:38.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great idea
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.66,0:01:39.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带他跟你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.66,0:01:39.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take him with you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.78,0:01:44.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我根本就不是那意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:44.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not what I had in mind
