Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.06,0:07:45.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把匹萨给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:45.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me the pizza
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.44,0:07:46.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下  我现在记起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:46.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, I remember now--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.77,0:07:47.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:47.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was coral
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.53,0:07:48.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把匹萨给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:48.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give it to me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.48,0:07:50.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不给  已经保证说是给客人的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:50.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, we promised it's for the customer
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.20,0:07:51.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:51.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是给客人的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's for the customer
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.99,0:07:54.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:54.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.95,0:07:57.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许最好要看一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:57.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe we better check on it--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.28,0:07:58.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,检查一下匹萨有没有事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:58.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make sure it's okay
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.29,0:08:00.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:00.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只看一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just a peek
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.66,0:08:02.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看完了  匹萨没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:02.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, it's fine
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.83,0:08:04.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  我应该看到了什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:04.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I think I saw something
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.79,0:08:06.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:06.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh no--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.21,0:08:08.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:08.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.59,0:08:09.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看起来应该没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:09.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks okay
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.88,0:08:13.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这匹萨长得可真是别致
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:13.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure is a fine-looking pizza
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.34,0:08:14.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:14.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.59,0:08:15.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:15.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.72,0:08:17.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是奶酪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:17.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that the cheese?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.93,0:08:18.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:18.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.97,0:08:21.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有辣香肠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:21.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the pepperoni?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.52,0:08:22.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:22.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.48,0:08:25.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看起来是不是很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:25.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks good, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a second
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.57,0:08:31.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道你要搞什么鬼了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:31.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know what you're trying to do, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.65,0:08:33.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是不会让你吃掉匹萨的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:33.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting you eat the pizza
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.53,0:08:34.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把匹萨给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:34.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that pizza
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.49,0:08:35.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:35.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别逼我直接用抢的  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't make me take it away from you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.95,0:08:39.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快起开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:39.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get away
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.79,0:08:41.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我回来  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:41.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back here, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.54,0:08:43.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把匹萨给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:43.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that pizza
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.25,0:08:44.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:44.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.33,0:08:46.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:46.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.96,0:08:47.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:47.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.00,0:08:50.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:50.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.50,0:08:51.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:51.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.05,0:08:55.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:55.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.34,0:08:57.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:57.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.39,0:08:59.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:08:59.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.39,0:09:01.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要那个匹萨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:01.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want that pizza
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.22,0:09:04.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不管怎样都要把匹萨给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:04.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you're going to hand it over one way or another
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看  我们得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, we're saved
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.56,0:09:07.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我们得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:07.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, we're saved
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.81,0:09:09.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在把匹萨给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:09.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now give me some pizza
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.19,0:09:09.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:09.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.52,0:09:10.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是真的  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:10.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really, squid
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.57,0:09:12.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:12.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're saved
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.86,0:09:14.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:14.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're saved
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.24,0:09:15.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能给我消停会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:15.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you cut that out
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.28,0:09:18.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得救了  得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:18.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Saved, saved
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.20,0:09:19.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得救了  得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:19.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Saved, saved
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.95,0:09:20.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得救了  得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:20.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Saved, saved
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.79,0:09:21.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得救了  得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:21.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Saved, saved
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得得得得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Saved, saved, saved, saved, saved, saved
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.29,0:09:24.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得得得得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:24.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Saved, saved, saved, saved, saved, saved
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得得得得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Saved, saved, saved, saved, saved, saved
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.50,0:09:27.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:27.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Saved, we are saved
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.13,0:09:30.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那只是块垃圾巨岩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:30.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's just a stupid boulder
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.96,0:09:33.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不只是块巨岩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:33.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not just a boulder
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.26,0:09:35.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是石头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:35.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a rock
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.42,0:09:36.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,石头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:36.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A rock
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.43,0:09:39.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,石头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:39.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A rock
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.47,0:09:46.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是巨大美丽又古老的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:46.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a big, beautiful old rock
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.31,0:09:50.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老祖先就用这些石头骑行了好几里远
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:50.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The pioneers used to ride these babies for miles
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.11,0:09:51.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且这石头形态绝佳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:51.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And it's in great shape
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.48,0:09:55.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  能不能别扯什么笨祖先了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:55.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you forget the stupid pioneers?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.53,0:09:58.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有没有想过老祖先现在一个不剩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:58.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you ever noticed that there are none of them left?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.57,0:10:00.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原因就在于他们打车技能差
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:00.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's because they were lousy hitchhikers
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.99,0:10:04.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还吃珊瑚  还用海藻看方向
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:04.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ate coral, and took directions from algae
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.20,0:10:06.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在你又跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:06.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now you're telling me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.29,0:10:08.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们还可以开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:08.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they thought they could drive
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.58,0:10:10.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,石头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:10.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rocks
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.96,0:10:12.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你等等我  叶忒罗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:12.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on there, Jethro
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.76,0:10:17.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我等不及要看客人脸上的表情了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:17.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to see the look on our customer's face
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.68,0:10:22.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:22.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.39,0:10:23.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恭喜你先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:23.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.76,0:10:25.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的蟹黄堡匹萨送到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:25.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your krabby patty pizza's here
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.48,0:10:26.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:26.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.98,0:10:28.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直都很想要来一份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:28.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been dying for one of these
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.31,0:10:28.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:28.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.35,0:10:30.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我饮料呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:30.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's my drink?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.15,0:10:32.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:32.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What drink?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.36,0:10:33.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我饮料呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:33.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My drink
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.90,0:10:35.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我无糖海草水呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:35.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My Diet Dr Kelp
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.69,0:10:38.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别跟我说你忘记送饮料来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:38.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you forgot my drink
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.15,0:10:39.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是  你根本就没有点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:39.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you didn't order any
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.86,0:10:43.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有饮料我还吃什么匹萨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:43.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to eat this pizza without my drink?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.83,0:10:44.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:44.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.54,0:10:47.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就没有给顾客着想过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:47.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Didn't you ever once think of the customer?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.37,0:10:49.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就这水平都能叫外卖员
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:49.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You call yourself a delivery boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.75,0:10:51.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那老子不买了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:51.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I ain't buying
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.71,0:10:53.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:53.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sponge?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.21,0:10:56.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:56.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sponge?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.96,0:10:58.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:58.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's okay
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.80,0:10:59.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:10:59.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.94,0:11:13.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:13.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sponge?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.28,0:11:21.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么又来一个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:21.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another one?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.78,0:11:24.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好  老子跟你同伴说了不付匹萨钱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:24.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, I told your little friend I ain't paying for that
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.49,0:11:26.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这份免费送
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:26.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, this one's on the house
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他改主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did he change his mind?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.50,0:11:30.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:30.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He sure did
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.04,0:11:32.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一口就把匹萨给吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:32.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ate the whole thing in one bite
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.88,0:11:33.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没配饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:33.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No drink?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.88,0:11:34.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没配
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:34.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在带我回家去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now take me home
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.05,0:11:36.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:36.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.05,0:11:39.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有足够时间回去上班呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:39.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have just enough time to make it back to work
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.63,0:11:42.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上班
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:42.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Work?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.64,0:11:47.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爪子好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:47.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My aching tentacles
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:54.19,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(315,313)}大菠萝\N{\fs30} \N{\fs150}甜蜜的家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:56.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(313.471,311.334)\frz11.85}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:59.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1094.478,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:56.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(378.763,686.667)\frz10.85}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:59.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(487.441,254)\frz14.7}编剧
