Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.40,0:12:08.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:08.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Walking
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.79,0:12:14.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,饿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:14.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.25,0:12:18.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是饿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:18.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Still hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.13,0:12:26.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是饿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:26.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Still hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.01,0:12:30.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,死线虫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:30.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dang nematodes
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.23,0:12:38.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,渴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:38.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thirsty
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:50.66,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(368.513,920)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.71,0:13:03.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:03.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurray, gary
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.05,0:13:04.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们终于变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:04.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're finally huge
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.30,0:13:07.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:07.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.85,0:13:17.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,贝壳电话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:17.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shell phone
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.11,0:13:18.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:18.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.90,0:13:19.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打电话给章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:19.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll call Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.69,0:13:20.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他知道要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:20.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He'll know what to do
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.36,0:13:22.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:22.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.07,0:13:23.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:23.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.32,0:13:26.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我搞破坏的时间到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:26.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is it time already for you to ruin my day?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.61,0:13:28.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  快来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:28.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, help me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.07,0:13:29.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我房子在变小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:29.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My house is shrinking
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.03,0:13:29.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一大早起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:29.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I woke up this morning
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.78,0:13:30.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,房子整个越变越小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:30.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and it was getting smaller and smaller
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.91,0:13:31.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,墙都要挤到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:31.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The walls are closing in on me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.79,0:13:32.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗也被吓着了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:32.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary is terrified too
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.33,0:13:35.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:35.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.17,0:13:37.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:37.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep, it is
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.25,0:13:42.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给章鱼哥搞破坏的时间到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:42.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is it time already to ruin Squid's day?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.05,0:13:48.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  别丢下我一个人开搞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:48.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, don't start without me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.31,0:14:00.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,线虫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:00.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nematodes
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.90,0:14:06.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我家剩下来的就只有这颗小石子了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:06.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The only thing left in my house is this little pebble
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.61,0:14:08.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这都怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:08.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.91,0:14:10.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位  我有个坏消息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:10.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got bad news, guys
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.82,0:14:12.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看我家怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:12.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at what happened to my house
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.58,0:14:13.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:13.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's gone
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all gone
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.00,0:14:18.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:18.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.54,0:14:19.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要去哪住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:19.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where am I going to live?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.96,0:14:21.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:21.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.96,0:14:26.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你家消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:26.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, your house is gone
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.51,0:14:27.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么说才好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:27.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, what can I say?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.47,0:14:28.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,认识你可真高兴  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:28.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's been great knowing you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.01,0:14:30.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你到别处好运
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:30.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good luck somewhere else
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.22,0:14:33.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会想你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:33.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to miss you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.35,0:14:42.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥好难接受这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:42.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squid's taking it real hard
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.15,0:14:45.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你现在要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:45.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.19,0:14:48.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看我得搬回去跟爸妈住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:48.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll have to move back with my mom and dad
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:50.86,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1023.141,958)}爸妈
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.91,0:14:51.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:51.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, wait a minute--
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.95,0:14:53.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以不用搬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:53.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, you don't
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:54.08,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1028.477,958)}爸妈
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.08,0:14:56.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱可以给你盖新房子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:56.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can build you a new house
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.41,0:14:58.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,房子咱盖不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:58.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can't build a house
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.29,0:15:00.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啦  很简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:00.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, sure, it's easy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我房子就是自己一个人盖的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I built my house all by myself
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.71,0:15:06.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就好  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:06.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.05,0:15:07.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来开工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:07.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get to work
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.51,0:15:52.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完工了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:52.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're done
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.51,0:15:53.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:53.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.80,0:15:55.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:55.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, what do you think?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.47,0:15:57.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真希望能住进去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:57.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish I lived there
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.14,0:15:59.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:15:59.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.77,0:16:00.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:00.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.19,0:16:03.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一室
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:03.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One bedroom
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.32,0:16:08.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真该死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:08.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tartar sauce
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.65,0:16:13.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像我们只能回去跟爸妈住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:13.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, looks like we've got to move back with mom and pop
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.57,0:16:15.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可以搬回去跟爸妈住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:15.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't move back in with your parents
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.03,0:16:18.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爸妈把我给赶出家门那会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:18.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When my parents kicked me out of the house
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.04,0:16:19.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就从来没回去过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:19.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never went back
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.58,0:16:20.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:20.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.66,0:16:23.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你跟小蜗可以来跟我一起住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:23.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You and Gary can come stay with me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.92,0:16:25.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:25.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That'd be great
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.29,0:16:26.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:26.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.04,0:16:27.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们就要变石友了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:27.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll be rockmates
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.05,0:16:32.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:32.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.14,0:16:37.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  石友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:37.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, rockmate
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.01,0:16:39.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:39.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.40,0:16:49.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞什
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:49.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the
