Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:18:57.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get them off
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.44,0:18:58.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:58.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wake up
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.07,0:18:59.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别打了  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:18:59.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, it's me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.11,0:19:00.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:00.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.80,0:19:22.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:22.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spider
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.43,0:19:23.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:23.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spider
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.30,0:19:24.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快弄下来
