Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.48,0:19:33.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:33.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.90,0:19:36.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:36.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.03,0:19:38.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:38.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.82,0:19:40.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:40.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.65,0:19:41.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:41.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.15,0:19:43.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们能在这待几天或者一两个月吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:43.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could we stay here a couple of days or a month or two?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.57,0:19:46.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能吧  随便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:46.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, whatever
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.33,0:19:47.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:47.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.00,0:19:49.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:49.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  可不可以移到旁边去一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, can you scoot over a little?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.83,0:19:53.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:53.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.42,0:19:56.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能顺便给我拿杯水来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:56.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, while you're at it, can you get me a glass of water?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.09,0:19:57.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:57.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.42,0:19:59.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:19:59.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.05,0:20:01.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你家真的好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:01.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is a real swell place you've got here
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.09,0:20:02.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢了  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:02.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.55,0:20:04.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:04.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're welcome
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.14,0:20:06.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好喜欢到别人家过夜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:06.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I like sleep-overs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.47,0:20:08.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:08.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.27,0:20:09.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:09.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me, too
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.06,0:20:12.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊  真的棒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:12.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep, this is great
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.48,0:20:13.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:13.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.15,0:20:16.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:16.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.24,0:20:23.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:23.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.71,0:20:36.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天是个好日子  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:36.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Today's the big day, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.13,0:20:38.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可别迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:38.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't want to be late
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.84,0:20:39.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得赶紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:39.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got to hurry
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.47,0:20:42.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:42.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.17,0:20:43.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都给我等下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:43.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold everything
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.22,0:20:47.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不想错过这场好戏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:47.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would not want to miss this--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.76,0:20:51.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝今天就要搬走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:51.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The day SpongeBob moves
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.27,0:20:54.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信这事真的发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:54.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it's really happening
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.64,0:20:56.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别担心了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:56.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.06,0:20:57.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会回来看你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:57.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll come visit you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.27,0:20:59.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用安慰我了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:20:59.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't try to cheer me up, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.86,0:21:00.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:00.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.74,0:21:02.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爸妈来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:02.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here come my parents
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.99,0:21:06.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:06.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.24,0:21:07.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乖宝贝好  我们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:07.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, honey, we're here
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.20,0:21:09.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快上车  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:09.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.70,0:21:11.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,儿子你要赶紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.70,0:21:11.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry, son
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.08,0:21:12.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你妈把饭都做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:12.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your mother has dinner waiting
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.91,0:21:13.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:13.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, mom
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.71,0:21:15.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵妈妈好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.71,0:21:15.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, Mrs. SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.92,0:21:17.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来帮你们提行李
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:17.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me help you with these bags
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.54,0:21:18.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:18.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just give me a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.34,0:21:23.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也留不住你了  小石子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:23.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I cannot hold on to you any longer, little pebble
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.72,0:21:34.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你留下了好多的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.72,0:21:34.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You hold too many memories
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.15,0:21:44.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.15,0:21:44.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.82,0:21:45.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就此再会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.82,0:21:45.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is good-bye
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.03,0:21:47.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:47.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.82,0:21:49.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:49.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.07,0:21:50.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:50.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.24,0:21:51.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:51.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye-bye
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.24,0:21:52.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:52.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.95,0:21:54.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:54.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye, good-bye
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.91,0:21:56.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快上车  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.91,0:21:56.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.67,0:21:57.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.67,0:21:57.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.88,0:22:00.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:00.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye, Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.42,0:22:06.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.42,0:22:06.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob is leaving
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.63,0:22:07.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要走了  要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.63,0:22:07.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's leaving, he's leaving
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.31,0:22:12.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是的宝贝儿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:12.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, baby
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.18,0:22:17.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.18,0:22:17.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob is leaving
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.44,0:22:18.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:18.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's leaving
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.87,0:22:33.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我家回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:33.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My house is back
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.95,0:22:37.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的菠萝屋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:37.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good old pineapple
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.79,0:22:39.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就刚好在原先的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.79,0:22:39.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was exactly where it used to be
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.09,0:22:47.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥你说好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.09,0:22:47.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, isn't this great?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.63,0:22:49.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也不走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.63,0:22:49.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm back forever
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.59,0:22:51.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也不走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.59,0:22:51.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forever?
